org.joyrest.routing

Class TypedControllerConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.joyrest.routing.AbstractControllerConfiguration
      • org.joyrest.routing.TypedControllerConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ControllerConfiguration

    public abstract class TypedControllerConfiguration
extends AbstractControllerConfiguration

    Class TypedControllerConfiguration is abstract implementation of ControllerConfiguration and makes easier to create the given route using predefined protected method.

    It can be considered as container for routes which are provided to RequestProcessor because of processing and handling incoming requests.

    Author:
    pbouda
    See Also:
    ControllerConfiguration, AbstractControllerConfiguration, Route
